{"tid":1652141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企個老豆啱啱講咗一番說話，巴絲幫手諗下點答","createTime":"2019-10-13T14:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:59:00.000Z","uid":203420,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f0171aea2cc5d5fce8897492f3dcdb957ea066","tid":1652141,"uid":203420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"家父淺黃，不過成日睇電視新聞都屌話發夢無用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />家父<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋後生仔咁樣出街邊有用啫，淨比人打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得咁講嘅，上街表達訴求，比人打係班狗發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錯不在我哋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有咩jetso先？人就比警察打曬，又要拉返警局打鑊甘，有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要keep住出聲㗎嘛，依家stop曬咁咪好似認輸？時代革命啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港尚有一絲法律啊 點解唔和平示威，咁咪唔會比人捉比人打。 十一月區議會選舉，你上個咩登叫班友投比自己人，踢班保皇黨落街咪仲好？成日睇你班𡃁仔比人拉好心痛㗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算你打爆曬成條街，都威脅唔到政權，香港又運唔得槍入來，啫無得打返轉頭啦。咁咪用投票來打政權囉！香港人又唔鍾意投票！<br />\n<br />\n好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹點應佢好？"},{"pid":"0775daad7917fea1d9a7abf5ccfec2b36ea678bb","tid":1652141,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"你d答案咪一樣係淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74c350029e792a6e7702de364b0d307d4498686","tid":1652141,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"